                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d444">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the <gloss type="to">American Minister</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1910-06-22">
                            <hi rend="italic">June 22, 1910</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Falkner’s appointment received and delivered. To avoid possible misunderstanding,
                    his designation and powers should be described in commission as quoted in
                    Department’s cable of June 18. Inform Liberian Government.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Wilson.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
